Name: Roadkill Raceway
About the game: In the not so distant future... the power of animal rights organizations has increased 10 fold. All animals are considered to have human level rights with one exception - getting in the way of a public service vehicle is not covered. You must help save the worlds food supply by testing out your vehicle. Farmers regularly bring animal shipments to the vehicle testing raceway for a 'tour' of the track. Game Features: 5 different tracks 4 different animals Currently one vehicle type High powered breaking and acceleration system Nitro - for a little extra boost once in a while
